values:
Ha, I figured this thing would have been deleted, or at least mothballed by now...I'm just sitting around at work, my codes are running and I've got about 18 hours of calculation time left...so I'm starving for something to do, hence, this thing.&nbsp; Bah.&nbsp; 
To all my friends back in indiana, I'm sorry i've been such a hermit the past year or so, but you know how I am, I may not keep up to date with you guys, but you're still my friends, and I miss the lot of ya.
If you're curious, and i'd assume if you're still reading this, you are, I'll be back to Purdue for one more semester this fall, and hopefully by then I'll have some gainful employment in that scary place we all know as the real world.&nbsp; For anyone who hasn't been out west, and has the time, I say you should take a road trip, and we'll take a weekend to show you the sights.&nbsp; I'm well out here, and my dear Janice is out here with me, along with the marley dogg, so I've got no complaints.&nbsp; Who knows, maybe i'll start posting on this again...heh...yeah right.
